WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.960
My name is Erin Henderson, and I am a teacher in the Phoenix Union High School District.

00:04.960 --> 00:09.280
I know Ty White through the Teacher of the Year program, and he asked me to come chaperone.

00:09.280 --> 00:14.760
As an English teacher, I had no idea what to expect, because these are science kids.

00:14.760 --> 00:20.720
But I can't believe the amount of English skills and life skills I saw within 24 hours

00:20.720 --> 00:22.720
with these students.

00:22.720 --> 00:24.600
They had to read technical writing.

00:24.600 --> 00:26.320
They had to write their own technical writing.

00:26.320 --> 00:28.920
They had to respond to an RFP.

00:28.920 --> 00:33.080
These students put together presentations and spoke eloquently in front of industry

00:33.080 --> 00:37.280
professionals who were judging the work they had done in just 24 hours.

00:37.280 --> 00:38.280
It was magic.

00:38.280 --> 00:40.920
The energy in these rooms, it was palpable.

00:40.920 --> 00:42.680
And I'm so honored to be a part of it.

00:42.680 --> 00:47.240
I can't wait to take it back to Phoenix Union and introduce this program to students in

00:47.240 --> 00:48.760
Phoenix to get them down here as well.

